        </svg>
        <span class="brand-text">Jerry &amp; Co.</span>
      </div>
      <p class="footer-blurb">
        Factory-grade cabinet refinishing and bathroom refresh for condo owners across Greater Boston — built around your building's rules, your neighbors, and your timeline.
      </p>
      <div class="footer-contact">
        <a href="tel:+13476026801">(347) 602-6801</a>
